public class ConstraintEvaluatedOnSinglePathNodeWithSingleCompareNodeEvent extends ConstraintEvaluatedOnSinglePathNodeEvent implements SingleCompareNodeEvent
Event emitted when a constraint is evaluated on a single value node with a single compare node. For example, when a LessThanConstraint is evaluated.
